@startuml component_architecture
!theme plain

title UIM Advanced Event Mesh (AEM) - Component Architecture

actor "EDA Architect / Integration Team" as User

node "AEM Service Runtime" {
  component "AEMServer\n(vibe.d REST API)" as Api
  component "AEMService\n(Streaming + Management + Monitoring)" as Domain
  database "AEMStore\n(In-Memory Data)" as Store
}

User --> Api : manage brokers, meshes, EDA, monitoring
Api --> Domain : routed use-case operations
Domain --> Store : persist/retrieve runtime data

note right of Domain
Capabilities:
- event streaming lifecycle
- event management modeling
- monitoring dashboards + notifications
end note

@enduml
